  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"KONKONKON\" is an adventure game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3572020/extras/8dda18db7e088f5730c5308ffee5ab08.avif?t=1768175052\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out of curiosity, I find myself walking toward the <strong>\"town where all the residents disappeared.\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, I can’t shake the eerie feeling of being watched… by something.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suddenly, I hear a noise and turn in that direction, just in time to see a small animal scurrying away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That was… a <strong>fox</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come to think of it, what sound do foxes make again…?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3572020/extras/a189ffdf019df2b4fbf82415f4d5674b.avif?t=1768175052\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A walking simulator where various events unfold as you explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress the story by examining objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No quest markers or time limits—enjoy the experience at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She has <strong>long ears</strong> and <strong>a tail</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime: 15 to 60 minutes</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming is allowed for both individuals and businesses <strong>without prior permission</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"KONKONKON\" is an adventure game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3572020/extras/8dda18db7e088f5730c5308ffee5ab08.avif?t=1768175052\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Out of curiosity, I find myself walking toward the <strong>\"town where all the residents disappeared.\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, I can’t shake the eerie feeling of being watched… by something.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suddenly, I hear a noise and turn in that direction, just in time to see a small animal scurrying away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That was… a <strong>fox</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come to think of it, what sound do foxes make again…?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3572020/extras/a189ffdf019df2b4fbf82415f4d5674b.avif?t=1768175052\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A walking simulator where various events unfold as you explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress the story by examining objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No quest markers or time limits—enjoy the experience at your own pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She has <strong>long ears</strong> and <strong>a tail</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime: 15 to 60 minutes</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming is allowed for both individuals and businesses <strong>without prior permission</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
